      "name": "Sinful Spoils Offenders",
      "effect": "If your opponent Special Summons a monster(s) from the Deck and/or Extra Deck and you control a \"Diabellstar\" Monster Card: Target 1 monster they control; shuffle it into the Deck. During the Damage Step, if your \"Diabellstar\" monster battles an opponent's monster: You can banish this card from your GY; that opponent's monster's ATK becomes halved until the end of this turn. You can only use each effect of \"Sinful Spoils Offenders\" once per turn.",
